_sText:
FIRSTLY, THANK you for downloading my map! ;-)

This map is the only Hoejhus map made with an maze. This map have two bombsites. Bombsite A is where it normaly is, but there is two ways to get down there now. Bombsite B is over the maze, and is surrended by some Fence. If you fall down and hit the ground, don't worry. You will be teleported to an Jail, with losing a bit health, dispends on how fast you are getting out ;-) There is also alot secret rooms in this map, good luck finding them ;-) 

You are more than welcome to join us at: 217.163.30.167:27015 - [DK] Hoejhus 24/7 |FFA - 100 TICK!|

You can also just join our SteamGroup: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/HoejhusServer

I hope you will Enjoy the map and I hope to see you soon on the server! ;-)
